<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Enrollment Confirmation - {{platformName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .success-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .success-banner h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .success-banner p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .course-card {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        }
        .course-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .course-image {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .course-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .course-info p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .course-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-item {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .detail-item .label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .detail-item .value {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .step-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .step-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        .step-list li:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .step-number {
            background-color: #2196f3;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .instructor-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .instructor-avatar {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #6c757d;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .instructor-details h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .instructor-details p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .payment-info {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .payment-info h4 {
            color: #155724;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .payment-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .payment-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            color: #155724;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .course-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .course-image {
                margin: 0 auto 15px auto;
            }
            .course-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .instructor-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .instructor-avatar {
                margin: 0 auto 15px auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">{{platformName}}</div>
            <h1 class="title">Enrollment Confirmed!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Welcome to your new learning journey</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="success-banner">
                <h2>üéâ Congratulations {{capitalize studentName}}!</h2>
                <p>You've successfully enrolled in your new course</p>
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for choosing {{platformName}} for your learning journey. We're excited to have you as part of our community!</p>

            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="course-header">
                    <div class="course-image">
                        {{#if courseImage}}
                        <img src="{{courseImage}}" alt="{{courseName}}" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px;">
                        {{else}}
                        üìö
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-info">
                        <h3>{{courseName}}</h3>
                        <p>{{courseDescription}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="course-details">
                    {{#if instructor}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Instructor</div>
                        <div class="value">{{instructor}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if duration}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Duration</div>
                        <div class="value">{{duration}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if startDate}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Start Date</div>
                        <div class="value">{{formatDate startDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if level}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Level</div>
                        <div class="value">{{capitalize level}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if totalLessons}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Lessons</div>
                        <div class="value">{{totalLessons}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if language}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="label">Language</div>
                        <div class="value">{{language}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if instructorInfo}}
            <div class="instructor-info">
                <div class="instructor-avatar">
                    {{#if instructorInfo.avatar}}
                    <img src="{{instructorInfo.avatar}}" alt="{{instructorInfo.name}}" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;">
                    {{else}}
                    üë®‚Äçüè´
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="instructor-details">
                    <h4>Meet Your Instructor: {{instructorInfo.name}}</h4>
                    <p>{{instructorInfo.bio}}</p>
                    {{#if instructorInfo.experience}}
                    <p><strong>Experience:</strong> {{instructorInfo.experience}}</p>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if paymentInfo}}
            <div class="payment-info">
                <h4>üí≥ Payment Confirmation</h4>
                <div class="payment-details">
                    {{#if paymentInfo.amount}}
                    <div class="payment-item">
                        <span>Amount Paid:</span>
                        <span><strong>{{formatCurrency paymentInfo.amount}}</strong></span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if paymentInfo.transactionId}}
                    <div class="payment-item">
                        <span>Transaction ID:</span>
                        <span>{{paymentInfo.transactionId}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if paymentInfo.method}}
                    <div class="payment-item">
                        <span>Payment Method:</span>
                        <span>{{paymentInfo.method}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if paymentInfo.date}}
                    <div class="payment-item">
                        <span>Payment Date:</span>
                        <span>{{formatDate paymentInfo.date}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}" class="cta-button">Start Learning Now</a>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>üöÄ What's Next?</h4>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Access Your Course:</strong> Click the button above or visit your dashboard to start learning immediately.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Download Materials:</strong> Access course materials, assignments, and resources from your course page.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Join the Community:</strong> Connect with fellow students in the course discussion forum.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Track Progress:</strong> Monitor your learning progress and complete assignments on time.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            {{#if additionalInfo}}
            <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0;">
                <h4 style="color: #856404; margin-top: 0;">üìã Important Information</h4>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin-bottom: 0;">{{additionalInfo}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>We're here to support you throughout your learning journey. If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

            <p>Happy learning!<br>
            <strong>The {{platformName}} Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Enrollment confirmation sent to {{studentEmail}}</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>Visit your <a href="{{baseUrl}}/dashboard">dashboard</a> to manage your courses</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{platformName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>